{"tid":837610,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[絕地求生]房門壞鎖之逃出生天","createTime":"2018-09-26T13:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T15:46:00.000Z","uid":35572,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2560d41599d1b05cd305ea049b05d0bc65e66c","tid":837610,"uid":35572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的 話說今日啊婆唔知做乜鳩扭爆咗個鎖#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />f <br />\n返到嚟嘅時候本身同老母一齊笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知啱啱食完飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入房嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚記得咗個鎖已經不復存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一嘢轟埋咗度門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身仲好淡定 心諗門把冇咗個鎖應該唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知居然 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">開唔倒門</span></em></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/212735_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F212735_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=087c4447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如題 而家仲係房入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103bb9fdee0dea1ce69854c9253dce1b41092580","tid":837610,"uid":35572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7349cf00afa5aca75f90a2542bec69